# Robots

Computer programs for use inside of OpenOS when using a robot.

## simpleMining.lua
A simple mining script that uses a generator upgrade and, if available, a chuncloader upgrade for mining tunnels autonomously.
It stops as soon as the inventory if filled up to the last slot or when there is no more energy or combustible material inside of the robot.

### Usage
```bash
simpleMining
```
Starts the mining process.
